# Design Decisions

## 1. Tech Stack Choices
- **Why React + Vite:** fast refresh, minimal config
- **Why Node.js & Express:** lightweight, SSE support

## 2. Database Selection
- **Postgres vs. NoSQL:** relational for user data, vector store for embeddings

## 3. LLM Integration
- **Gemini Flash** vs. OpenAI GPT: cost, latency, on-prem fallback

## 4. Authentication & Security
- JWT in SameSite-Strict cookies, CSRF considerations

## 5. Trade-offs
- Server-side rendering vs. SPA
- Monolithic repo vs. microservices
